<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5966] Admin UI - menu is fixed, doesn&apos;t respect smaller viewports</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5966</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am a window 7 user, i am new in solr, i downloaded the setup for solr 4.7.1 and when i start the server and opened the admin interface using this url: &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/collection1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/collection1&lt;/a&gt;, then I noticed that on selecting the collection1 from cores  menu, I was unable to view the full list for collection1.&lt;br/&gt;
Please find this google doc link &lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5GzwVkR3aDzNzJheHVmWFRFYzA/edit?usp=sharing&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5GzwVkR3aDzNzJheHVmWFRFYzA/edit?usp=sharing&lt;/a&gt; containing the screenshot.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Operating system: windows 7 64-bit, hard disk - 320GB, Memory - 3GB&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
